org.anchoranalysis.feature.session.cache.finder

Class CheckCacheForSpecificChildren

  • Object
    • CheckCacheForSpecificChildren
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChildCacheFinder

    public class CheckCacheForSpecificChildren
extends Object
implements ChildCacheFinder
    For particular child-caches, check if a session-input is available from another LRU-cache and reuse.

    This is used to "redirect" certain child-caches to reuse sessions elsewhere.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
